{"tid":391063,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超提早關閉夏季轉會窗？😱","createTime":"2017-09-07T13:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T14:10:07.000Z","uid":8588,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ed69358d8f1add0e15a55b1e7963adaf3c84b028","tid":391063,"uid":8588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:34:49.000Z","msg":"BREAKING: Premier League teams vote to close summer transfer window before the season starts #SSN"},{"pid":"5c9d6e673c082489924e00d8f39826e57341bd1f","tid":391063,"uid":2545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"Premier League clubs have voted to close next summer's transfer window before the season starts.<br />\n<br />\nManagers have complained that the ability for players to move when the season is under way causes disruption to their squads and preparations.<br />\n<br />\nFrom next season, the window will close at 17:00 BST on the Thursday before the Premier League season begins.<br />\n<br />\nThe decision was not unanimous and does not impact upon the length of the window in the Football League.<br />\n<br />\nBut the move means Premier League clubs will not be able to sign or sell players when their season is under way, while other European leagues will continue to allow such movement until 31 August."},{"pid":"dadbb982b3a02613a7bb42a814d2ffae8cd49407","tid":391063,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:40:10.000Z","msg":"cloud add最開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2523da5fa7cb4891fedac4d23739e0f2f6419637","tid":391063,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:41:52.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faaa3e05d0f3d018af6ff556c19d73d4db694ed1","tid":391063,"uid":31652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>cloud add最開